Must Have:
As a user I would like to be able to rank the issues in sustainability that are most important to me so I'll be able to choose which bank I want for personal banking.

Should Have:
Services offered by the banks: online banking, branches, cost
Further breakdown of non-green financing the banks engage in, eg. coal power, fracking, etc. from fossil fuel financing.

Could Have:
Further links or descriptions to the bank's pledges and reports to investigate myself.
Easy to see red flags for key issues
Ability to choose issues to flag.

Won't Have:
Explanations of sustainability strategies/certifications/issues. 
